 or some blasted thing, I wouldn't take it. Wanted to send me to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}America{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Dr. Otley's what did it, had he used t
